title: Crochet with Bits & Pieces
description: Everyone has them-those little bits and snippets of yarn left over from other projects. What to do with them? Add this book, and make almost anything! This amazing collection of projects uses up your stash and make fun, attractive projects to give away as gifts or to keep. There's a little bit of something for everyone here, from babies and kids to teens and adults, plus accessories for the home! Crochet enthusiasts from beginner to advanced will find a project to suit their fancy in this crochet library essential.
